2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel deep hybrid model that enhances and explores convolutional features for scene recognition. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with deep learning techniques for image classification. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with scene recognition using image features. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper deals with encoding image features into a fixed-length representation for efficient retrieval.
